Moods as told by Jake Gyllenhaal

Channing Tatum on his dad finding out he was a stripper in his past:
CT: “That was my very first time on your show (The Ellen DeGeneres Show), and I got to let you know that, that was the very first time that my dad actually found out that I was a stripper for a short time.”
I: “wait your dad didn’t know you were a stripper until that day? How did he take it? “
CT: “not well... really not well.”
